    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Agro World Order Intake V8.1\n\n**Drop-in Code nodes:**\n- Normalize Email → lib/normalize_email.js\n- Already Processed? → lib/dedupe.js\n- HPT Parser → lib/hpt.js (Emstek rule)\n- Customer Router → lib/customers.js (10 deterministic mappers)\n- Validate Upload → lib/validate_upload.js\n- Finalize Import → lib/finalize.js\n\n**Before running:**\n1. Replace 'Processed Hits' Set stub with a Data Table → Search row lookup.\n2. Replace 'Track Processed (last write)' Code node body with a Data Table → Insert row.\n3. Set `client_folder_id` and `review_folder_id` per customer (Memory / Load Memory).\n4. Confirm the three credential IDs still resolve:\n   - Microsoft Outlook account 2\n   - Qargo_Api_Key\n   - Anthropic account\n\nSee PATCHES.md §B for the per-node migration plan.",
        "height": 400,
        "width": 420
      },
